## Cohort discovery — tree hop indentation: nest hops under their parent

Context

The first tree-renderer pass put every hop as a direct sibling of
the rule's source node, so a 2-hop path drew both connectors off
the same trunk:

  ● Person  source
  │
  ├ via PhasProject ↓
  │ ○ Project [×]
  │
  ├ via hasComplianceType ↓        ← wrong — should branch from
  │ ⚑ ComplianceType [×]            Project, not Person

Sequential paths are *chained*, not parallel. Hop N's source is hop
N-1's target — the trunk should step rightward at every hop.

Fix

1. src/front/static/query/js/query-cohorts.js
   - ``_renderHopRow`` now emits an empty
     ``.cohort-tree-hops-children`` container at the end of every
     hop's wrapper.
   - ``_renderLinkCard`` walks the path and appends each hop into
     the *previous* hop's children container (instead of all into
     the root list), producing nested DOM:
       root → hop0 → children → hop1 → children → hop2 …
     The trunk on each level naturally indents under the parent's
     bullet because the children container is part of the parent's
     subtree.

2. src/front/static/query/css/query-cohorts.css
   - Trunk ``margin-left`` reduced from ``0.65rem`` to ``0.35rem``
     so the dashed line passes through the bullet center on every
     level.
   - ``.cohort-tree-hops:not(:empty)`` keeps the dashed border
     scoped to non-empty containers — the terminal hop's own
     children container is empty and renders nothing.
   - ``.cohort-tree-hops-children:not(:empty)`` gets a small
     negative ``margin-top`` so the trunk visually starts from the
     parent bullet rather than from below the where pane.
   - Restored ``.cohort-tree-hop-terminal::after`` mask so a
     terminal hop with a tall where pane doesn't leave a stray
     trunk segment trailing past the flag.

Result

  ● Person  source
  │
  └ via PhasProject ↓
    ○ Project [×]
    │
    └ via hasComplianceType ↓     ← now branches off Project
      ⚑ ComplianceType  shared

Files modified
  - src/front/static/query/js/query-cohorts.js
  - src/front/static/query/css/query-cohorts.css

Tests
  - Cohort suite: 99 / 99 passed (DOM is rendering-only, no
    behavioural change).
