============================================================
Cohort Discovery — sample-values picker modal
============================================================

Context

The "list available values" button on every "equal to"
filter (both per-hop where rows and rule-level compatibility
rows) was firing ``window.prompt`` with a numbered text dump:

  Pick a value (or paste one):
  1. Active
  2. Inactive
  3. Pending
  …

That UX is jarring inside a Bootstrap-styled app, doesn't
respect dark mode, and the user has to type the index or paste
