inside `.cursor/05-code-style-and-structure.mdc § Frontend (HTML/CSS/JS)`
and covered structure (no inline CSS/JS, asset folder layout) but not
visual language. Two design-token systems coexist in the codebase
(`--db-*` for the app shell, `--ovz-*` for the OntoViz canvas) and a
deliberate "Bootstrap colored buttons forced to grey" override lives in
`components.css` — none of this was documented for agents, who would
otherwise re-introduce coloured buttons or hard-coded hex values.

