     rule, the colour palette table, the explicit list of where primary
     red is allowed (and the "no coloured buttons" rule), typography
     and iconography (system font stack, Bootstrap Icons only), layout
     primitives (`.content-wrapper`, `.sidebar-layout`), the `ob-*` /
     `ovz-*` component naming convention, the catalog of reusable
     components already in the codebase (`ob-kpi-tile`,
