     (`dry-run`, `materialize`, `class-stats`, `edge-count`,
     `node-count`, `path-trace`, `sample-values`, `explain`) now
     receives `body: dict = Depends(cohort_json_body), ctx:
     CohortEngineContext = Depends(cohort_engine_context)`,
     reducing each handler to its actual business call.
   - The non-engine cohort routes (`list-rules`, `upsert-rule`,
